le=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: white; border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\"/><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: white; border: 1px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\">Options: <a href=\"#opt-item.data-delivery.archive\">1 option</a><br/>Initial Value: Coding = <a href=\"CodeSystem-nasa-data-archive-cs.html\" title=\"https://mitre.org/fhir/space-health/CodeSystem/nasa-data-archive-cs\">NASA Medical Data Archive Systems</a>#mmis \"Medical Mission Information System\"</td></tr>#xD;\n<tr><td colspan=\"6\" class=\"hierarchy\"><br/><a href=\"https://hl7.org/fhir/R4/formats.html#table\" title=\"Legend for this format\"><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"doco\" style=\"background-color: inherit\"/> Documentation for this format</a></td></tr></table><hr/><p><b>Options Sets</b></p><a name=\"opt-item.overview.sponsor\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for overview.sponsor </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">https://mitre.org/fhir/space-health/CodeSystem/nasa-mrid-sponsor-cs#ascr (\"Astronaut Strength Conditioning and Rehabilitation\")</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.overview.discipline\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for overview.discipline </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">https://mitre.org/fhir/space-health/CodeSystem/nasa-mrid-discipline-cs#reconditioning (\"Reconditioning\")</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.initial-assessment.orthostatic-status\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for initial-assessment.orthostatic-status </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">No orthostatic intolerance</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Mild orthostatic symptoms</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Moderate orthostatic symptoms</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Significant orthostatic intolerance</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.initial-assessment.gait-stability\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for initial-assessment.gait-stability </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Normal</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Mildly unsteady</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Moderately unsteady</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Significantly impaired</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.initial-assessment.muscle-soreness\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for initial-assessment.muscle-soreness </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">None</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Mild</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Moderate</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Severe</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.weekly-progress.balance-status\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for weekly-progress.balance-status </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Returned to normal</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Improving</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Stable</li><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">Requires intervention</li></ul><a name=\"opt-item.data-delivery.archive\"> </a><p><b>Answer options for data-delivery.archive </b></p><ul><li style=\"font-size: 11px\">https://mitre.org/fhir/space-health/CodeSystem/nasa-data-archive-cs#mmis (\"Medical Mission Information System\")</li></ul></div>"^^rdf:XMLLiteral ]
